{"id":"entities/buzz-access","title":"Buzz Access","type":"entities","html":"<blockquote>\n<p>Stub. <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/round-rock-tx\">Round Rock</a>-based LLC where <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/yahir-gonzalez\">Yahir</a> applied for a part-time Marketing Coordinator role on Oct 7, 2025 (<a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"summaries/2025-10-07-buzz-access-cover-letter\">2025 10 07 buzz access cover letter</a>). Stack mentioned: <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/hubspot\">HubSpot</a>, PageFly, One Click Upsell, <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/clickup\">ClickUp</a>, Slack, <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/facebook-ads\">Facebook Ads</a>, Klaviyo. A <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"concepts/bridge-income-strategies\">bridge income</a> target.</p>\n</blockquote>\n","related":[{"id":"entities/aeo-agency","label":"AEO Agency"},{"id":"concepts/bridge-income-strategies","label":"Bridge Income Strategies"},{"id":"summaries/2025-10-07-buzz-access-cover-letter","label":"Buzz Access Cover Letter — Marketing Coordinator pitch"},{"id":"entities/clickup","label":"ClickUp"},{"id":"entities/facebook-ads","label":"Facebook Ads"},{"id":"entities/hubspot","label":"HubSpot"},{"id":"entities/round-rock-tx","label":"Round Rock, TX"},{"id":"entities/yahir-gonzalez","label":"Yahir Gonzalez"}]}
